ActCanadian Dairy Commission Act
PrecisReappointment of JOHN CORE of Guelph, Ontario, as Chief Executive Officer of the Canadian Dairy Commission to hold office during pleasure, on a part-time basis, for a term ending on December 31, 2011, or until a new Chief Executive Director is appointed, whichever is earlier, effective October 7, 2011.
